---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro'
---
<DocsLayout title="Coverflow Effect">
  <h1>Coverflow Effect</h1>
  <p class="lead">An iTunes-style coverflow that rotates and depth-shifts side slides around the active one. Uses <code>rotateY</code> and <code>translateZ</code> to create a perspective fan of cards.</p>

  <h2>Import</h2>
  <pre><code>import {"{"} coverflowEffect {"}"} from '@andresclua/sliderkit-effects'</code></pre>

  <h2>Options</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Option</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>rotate</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>50</code></td><td>Degrees of Y-axis rotation applied per offset step from the active slide.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>stretch</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>0</code></td><td>Additional Z translate reduction per offset step, pulling side slides further back.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>depth</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>100</code></td><td>Base Z-depth offset. Higher values push inactive slides further behind the active one.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>modifier</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>1</code></td><td>Multiplier applied to the per-slide offset before rotation and depth calculations.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>slideShadows</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td>—</td><td>Reserved for per-slide shadow overlays.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <p>For each slide at offset <code>o</code> from the active index, the plugin computes:</p>
  <pre><code>{`rotateY(o * modifier * rotate deg)
translateZ(depth - |o| * depth px)
scaleX(1 - |o| * 0.1)
z-index: 100 - |o|`}</code></pre>

  <h2>Example</h2>
  <pre><code>{`import { createSlider } from '@andresclua/sliderkit'
import { coverflowEffect } from '@andresclua/sliderkit-effects'
import { arrows } from '@andresclua/sliderkit-plugins'

createSlider('#my-slider', {
  loop: true,
  plugins: [
    coverflowEffect({ rotate: 50, depth: 100 }),
    arrows(),
  ],
})
`}</code></pre>

  <pre><code>{`/* CSS */
.c--slider-effect-coverflow .c--slider-a__item {
  transition: transform 500ms ease;
}
`}</code></pre>

  <p><a href="/demos/effect-coverflow">View coverflow effect demo</a></p>
</DocsLayout>
